name.k: 星空 - 让您不再迷失

platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 星や惑星を見つけましょう！

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 觀摩美麗星宿，展開天體冒險
仰观星云变化 探访宇宙奥秘
自分だけのプラネタリウム
觀賞美麗星宿 展開天體冒險

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: This planetarium in your pocket makes it easy to discover the wonders of space wherever you go. Day or night, just aim your device skyward to see a live 3D map of the heavens, complete with beautifully illustrated constellations, stars, planets, and satellites. A special night mode helps you read the map in the dark, while integrated weather reports show the best times for stargazing. You can even have notifications alert you to future astronomical events.
這款 App 猶如一座可隨身攜帶的太空館，不管身處何方，都能輕鬆探索太空奇觀。無論日夜，只要將你的裝置對準天空，即可查看即時 3D 星圖。
太阳落山后，就让星星为你指引方向。无论走到哪里，这个口袋天文馆都能带你领略星空奇观。举起设备，App 就能快速识别恒星、行星、星座和卫星，带你尽享探索宇宙的乐趣。
This planetarium in your pocket makes it easy to discover the wonders of space wherever you go. Day or night, aim your device skyward to see a live 3D map of the heavens.
ポケットに入るプラネタリウムがあれば、どこからでも宇宙の不思議を簡単に発見できます。昼夜を問わず、デバイスを空に向ければ、天空の3Dマップがライブ表示されます。

This planetarium in your pocket makes it easy to discover the wonders of space wherever you go. Day or night, just aim your device skyward to see a live 3D map of the heavens, complete with beautifully illustrated constellations, stars, planets and satellites. A special night mode helps you read the map in the dark, while integrated weather reports show the best times for stargazing. You can even have notifications alert you to future astronomical events.
有了這款 App，就像是口袋裡裝了一座天文館。無論白天還是夜晚，你只要把裝置對準天空，就能觀看實時的 3D 星圖，探索宇宙之美。

Ce planétarium de poche vous permet de découvrir les merveilles de l’espace de partout. De jour comme de nuit, orientez votre appareil vers le ciel pour admirer une carte 3D en direct de la voûte céleste.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Step through a portal and experience the universe in AR.
プラネタリウムを携帯してARで宇宙を体験しよう。
Partez à la découverte de l’univers grâce à l’AR.
